casebody.data:
No. 192,

Misc.

Carengella v. United States. George F. Callaghan and George M. Crane for petitioner.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied for the reason that application therefor was not made within the time provided by law. Rule 37 (b) (2) of the Rules of Criminal Procedure.
